blockquote><br />\n卡多盃真係可以取代AZ甚至鐵血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a0de7bbf8e8c1541026b754ba37bf74401a642","tid":421362,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同卡多比<br />\n<br />\n真係冇一套入流<br />\n<br />\n揀出來侮辱左個盃字</blockquote><br />\n卡多盃真係可以取代AZ甚至鐵血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下下拎套大粒野出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8940de9c82208edbf77d549d83c8526a2deb972","tid":421362,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:10:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同卡多比<br />\n<br />\n真係冇一套入流<br />\n<br />\n揀出來侮辱左個盃字</blockquote><br />\n卡多盃真係可以取代AZ甚至鐵血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下下拎套大粒野出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真當年睇AZ結局係嬲咗陣<br />\n但諗深層都叫合理<br />\n<del>作為毒撚見到女神最後都係唔理兵仔當然感同身受</del><br />\n<br />\n睇到鐵血已經打個凸<br />\n心諗屌那星岡媽長井你地又short撚咗邊條筋<br />\n<br />\n點知一山還有一山高<br />\n睇卡多頭幾集正正常常<br />\n後面已經唔係暴走咁簡單<br />\n直頭係宇宙大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老老柒柒佢可以爆成咁都算係成就嚟<br />\n真係應該直接用卡多盃取代AZ盃"},{"pid":"9f72671e85a2db2a95f05d389d35e71b36b1a89d","tid":421362,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暫時廿個回覆：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/225452_dcb6cd6f2ae6a37a73a625d7b8cbe34f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F225452_dcb6cd6f2ae6a37a73a625d7b8cbe34f.png&h=6b43bf5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明明異世界電話咁好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個投票入面有樣嘢想提出嘅<br />\n就係有啲番我冇睇過，或者淨係睇過一兩集，好難就咁下判斷話佢好唔好睇<br />\n<br />\n好似智能手機我淨係睇咗頭一集5分鐘就棄咗番（因為一睇就知冇興趣），所以根本判斷唔到呢套個劇情係點"},{"pid":"80058b4394d26f1ef12a18fe46e1f430e68b88ab","tid":421362,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:49:15.000Z","msg":"今季az杯真係冇咩人選<br />\n大河內最尾兩集都唔係大河內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf682a8ac5faaea2448e1ca59e2c06355fff2ce","tid":421362,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今季az杯真係冇咩人選<br />\n大河內最尾兩集都唔係大河內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁即係要有從缺先得"},{"pid":"e773ab07718b1cd7b1667762ac4d52c21f5c987a","tid":421362,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:37:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>暫時廿個回覆：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/225452_dcb6cd6f2ae6a37a73a625d7b8cbe34f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F225452_dcb6cd6f2ae6a37a73a625d7b8cbe34f.png&h=6b43bf5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明明異世界電話咁好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個投票入面有樣嘢想提出嘅<br />\n就係有啲番我冇睇過，或者淨係睇過一兩集，好難就咁下判斷話佢好唔好睇<br />\n<br />\n好似智能手機我淨係睇咗頭一集5分鐘就棄咗番（因為一睇就知冇興趣），所以根本判斷唔到呢套個劇情係點</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 盡量投自己睇曬既？"},{"pid":"b23d53f0f0e3a47d99f20d753c830748b1cc2cbe","tid":421362,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:39:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同卡多比<br />\n<br />\n真係冇一套入流<br />\n<br />\n揀出來侮辱左個盃字</blockquote><br />\n卡多盃真係可以取代AZ甚至鐵血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下下拎套大粒野出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真當年睇AZ結局係嬲咗陣<br />\n但諗深層都叫合理<br />\n<del>作為毒撚見到女神最後都係唔理兵仔當然感同身受</del><br />\n<br />\n睇到鐵血已經打個凸<br />\n心諗屌那星岡媽長井你地又short撚咗邊條筋<br />\n<br />\n點知一山還有一山高<br />\n睇卡多頭幾集正正常常<br />\n後面已經唔係暴走咁簡單<br />\n直頭係宇宙大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老老柒柒佢可以爆成咁都算係成就嚟<br />\n真係應該直接用卡多盃取代AZ盃</blockquote><br />\n爛尾見識唔少，但爛尾爛到有種震撼嘅感覺，卡多應該係第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f64b8a03054ab946312e27d803656101cf80c9","tid":421362,"uid":35556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同卡多比<br />\n<br />\n真係冇一套入流<br />\n<br />\n揀出來侮辱左個盃字</blockquote><br />\n卡多盃真係可以取代AZ甚至鐵血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下下拎套大粒野出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真當年睇AZ結局係嬲咗陣<br />\n但諗深層都叫合理<br />\n<del>作為毒撚見到女神最後都係唔理兵仔當然感同身受</del><br />\n<br />\n睇到鐵血已經打個凸<br />\n心諗屌那星岡媽長井你地又short撚咗邊條筋<br />\n<br />\n點知一山還有一山高<br />\n睇卡多頭幾集正正常常<br />\n後面已經唔係暴走咁簡單<br />\n直頭係宇宙大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老老柒柒佢可以爆成咁都算係成就嚟<br />\n真係應該直接用卡多盃取代AZ盃</blockquote><br />\n爛尾見識唔少，但爛尾爛到有種震撼嘅感覺，卡多應該係第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔係爛尾咁簡單,去到中後期突然將前半建立既野全部毀於一旦只能夠寫個服字<br />\n由談判變成格劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7739832dda7e81816955e738ebc72b407500017b","tid":421362,"uid":5590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:02:21.000Z","msg":"az整體水準幾高，有齊商業片的要求，孤兒前段都叫有血有淚，打得精彩。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母卡多，明明全劇主題係交流，忽然生個女秒殺完場，今天的我打倒昨天的我，果然暴力係解決問題的最好方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e24e76b59ba55c4ed9bf7203917ff45f4bf81c","tid":421362,"uid":121255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:03:40.000Z","msg":"改名做卡多盃+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8eb268961e075d9c1d13a3267c49497c640991","tid":421362,"uid":23086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:27:35.000Z","msg":"但係我覺得叫A/Z盃有紀念性質<br />\n此終佢係初代 個種震撼情度唔係講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋如果之後有野勁過卡多咁又要改名"},{"pid":"926334edc18ba6c333fbb13a8a3828f9f3ebd1ee","tid":421362,"uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:30:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係我覺得叫A/Z盃有紀念性質<br />\n此終佢係初代 個種震撼情度唔係講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋如果之後有野勁過卡多咁又要改名</blockquote><br />\n咪係<br />\n其實我一路都講話應該要留番個名<br />\n始終初代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"accc85e98c436d21e4c1511493ce0a6730051528","tid":421362,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:09:41.000Z","msg":"毒撚台原來得50幾條友"},{"pid":"ca29b8a60d4e114378ef